			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>EQAL Media</strong> seeks a <strong>Visual Designer</strong> with experience designing websites and mobile experiences. We offer a creative and flexible working environment along with great benefits and competitive compensation. You would be joining a team of creative and smart interactive designers working together to bring the best user experience possible to our&nbsp; popular websites.</p>
<p>
<strong>RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p>
<p>
Our ideal Visual Designer thrives in a collaborative work environment. You have an eye for design and an aesthetic that is flexible in beauty &amp; fashion, food and parenting.</p>
<ul>
<li>
Collaborates with Product Manager and Design Director on strategy and design direction to achieve business goals</li>
<li>
Research, Mood Boards, Branding, Typography and Design comps</li>
<li>
Communicates design ideas with the engineering team (front end development)</li>
<li>
Works with a core team of design directors, product managers, engineers and editorial staff to deliver designs</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>SKILLS &amp; QUALIFICATIONS</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
3-6 years experience designing web and mobile experiences</li>
<li>
Responsive Design experience is a MUST</li>
<li>
App design experience (iOS) is a MUST</li>
<li>
Passionate about Design and stays current with Design Trends</li>
<li>
Proactive &quot;can do&quot; approach to new projects and subsequent revisions</li>
<li>
Ability to articulate concepts and ideas to the team</li>
<li>
Detail-oriented with strong organizational skills</li>
<li>
Clean aesthetic, fashion and beauty is a plus</li>
<li>
Experience with Photoshop, Illustrator</li>
<li>
Portfolio that demonstrates your ability to design beautiful and meaningful websites</li>
</ul>
